  "text": "The introduction of weights by [CITATION_1] enabled the consideration of trade-offs and adopted the weak interpretation of sustainability. Therefore, crucial conditions of the interpretations of the trade-offs between sustainability dimensions have been fixed already. Nevertheless, as the two concepts-the LCSA framework and the PSB-are independent from each other, the evaluation logic of the LCSA framework does not influence the way that the PSB can be applied.",
